OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FStiff Person Syndrome (SPS) is a rare
OL,7,Fneurological condition that can take
OL,8,Fyears to diagnose and requires
OL,9,Ftailored treatment.
OL,11,FIn 2022, singer Celine Dion revealed
OL,12,Fshe had been diagnosed with SPS, which
OL,13,Fcauses spasms that affect her ability
OL,14,Fto walk and sing.
OL,16,FShe has remained largely out of the
OL,17,Fspotlight since and was forced to
OL,18,Fcancel her Courage World Tour in 2023
OL,19,Fafter experiencing difficulties living
OL,20,Fwith the condition.
