OL,6,FBut on Saturday, she said she is
OL,7,F"deeply grateful" for the support from
OL,8,Fher family and fans as she opened up
OL,9,Fabout her experience of SPS.
OL,11,FShe wrote on Instagram: "Trying to
OL,12,Fovercome this autoimmune disorder has
OL,13,Fbeen one of the hardest experiences of
OL,14,Fmy life, but I remain determined to
OL,15,Fone day get back onto the stage and to
OL,16,Flive as normal of a life as possible."
