OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FSome develop a "statue-like"
OL,7,Fappearance due to the rigidity.
OL,9,FMany also experience painful muscle
OL,10,Fspasms that can last a few minutes to
OL,11,Fseveral hours and may affect the whole
OL,12,Fbody or certain muscles. The spasms
OL,13,Fcan be triggered by unexpected loud
OL,14,Fnoises, minor physical contact, cold
OL,15,Fenvironments, stress, or situations
OL,16,Fthat cause heightened emotions, says
OL,17,Fthe NORD.
