OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FSpasms in the chest and respiratory
OL,7,Fmuscles can be serious and require
OL,8,Fventilation or emergency treatment,
OL,9,Fwhile spasms in the legs often lead to
OL,10,Ffalls.
OL,12,FExperts still do not know the exact
OL,13,Fcause of SPS and it is often
OL,14,Funderdiagnosed.
OL,16,FWho is affected by Stiff Person
OL,17,FSyndrome?
