OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FThe condition is twice as likely to
OL,7,Faffect females than males, according
OL,8,Fto the National Institute of
OL,9,FNeurological Disorders and Stroke.
OL,11,FIt is frequently associated with other
OL,12,Fautoimmune diseases such as type-I
OL,13,Fdiabetes, thyroiditis, vitiligo, and
OL,14,Fpernicious anemia.
OL,16,FThe condition only occurs in about one
OL,17,Fin every million people.JHow is Stiff
OL,18,FPerson Syndrome treated?
