OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FThere is no cure for SPS but
OL,7,Ftreatment, such as anti-seizure drugs,
OL,8,Fpainkillers and anti-anxiety
OL,9,Fmedication, can help lessen symptoms.
OL,11,FThe condition is thought to have
OL,12,Ffeatures of an autoimmune disease,
OL,13,Faccording to the National Institute of
OL,14,FNeurological Disorders and Stroke.
OL,16,FSeveral symptoms improve with anti-
OL,17,Fanxiety and muscle relaxant drugs, or
OL,18,Fwith drugs that alleviate muscle
OL,19,Fspasms, such as baclofen or gabapentin.
